Summary: Taking pic of the new Dallas Stadium in Arlington, didn't know I captured this object in the background.
divs: sighting detailstaking a picture of stadium in arlington. loaded pic onto my pc at home, uploaded to my website http:\\www.cox2020.net . didn't enlarge the pic until this morning may 25,2009 and noticed the dot to the left side of stadium above small cloud. blew it up to 800% in picasa and it sure doesn't look like a plane or a bird. not sure what it is.
